==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Workmanly
<hw>Work"man*ly</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Becoming a skillful workman;
skillful; well performed; workmanlike.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Workmanly</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Workmanly
<hw>Work"man*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>In a skillful manner; in a
manner becoming a skillful workman.</def> <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Workmanship</ent>⟦br⟧
